summary: This adds a save game of mine where you have a blank character, to start off and change if wanted with the showracemenu console command!
descriptionHtml:
This characters name is Eoul-hea, Which means \"he who fled from helgen\" in argonian ;)
In his inventory you\'ll find all the armor (heavy/light/magecloth) and 2 1-handed weapons for you dual-wielders, a shield and a 2-handed weapon.
You start directly after the escape from the cave with most of the things you can pick up and get while escaping. 

NO extra\'s added :)

All you have to do is type showracemenu in the console and change the character to your likes!

Endorse, if you think this mod is usefull, please :)
author: Jojo4u
